---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 464
  - Title: Rig-Veda
    Location: VII 104 8
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=The Powers of Darkness
---
Whoever, when I am acting with pure and single heart, works against me
with charms that are counter to the rta (anrta), may he, O Indra, as
he pronounces non-existence (asat), himself go to non-existence, like
waters held in the fist.
